<section id="ctr_ref">
  <title>ctr_ref</title>
  <para>Reference - Holds a reference to a single instance of an element that has multiple instances
    within the enclosing element.</para>
  <para><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><emphasis>Type:</emphasis>
    string.</para><?oxy_custom_end?>
  <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis>
    NMTOKEN<?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?>: a string matching
    the pattern <code>[-._:A-Za-z0-9]+</code>.<?oxy_custom_end?></para>
  <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> undefined.</para>
  <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis><olink targetdoc="../../elements/change-tracking/revisions.xml"
      targetptr="revisions"><code>ctr_revisions</code></olink></para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <title>Constraints</title>
    <listitem>
      <para> The value of the <link linkend="ctr_ref"><code>ref</code></link> attribute
          <glossterm>must</glossterm> be the value of the <olink targetdoc="../../attributes/id.xml"
          targetptr="id"><code>id</code></olink> attribute of a single instance of an element that
        is a multiple instance within the enclosing element.</para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
</section>
